ction fan or open a window to avoid any strong fumes.","Use any remaining glaze to drizzle over salads, serve with bread and olive oil or use with dessert dishes featuring berries.","Cut your ciabatta into thick or thin slices, depending on how many people you are serving."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","4h 30m","25 pieces"]}